workflow Test Fix Workout
runner deepseek

agent analyze-test-results
title Analyze test results
prompt You are a test analysis expert. Examine the file `test-results.log`. List every failing test, its error message, and your assessment of likely root causes. Keep your summary concise and actionable.
after none

agent pick-test-to-fix
title Pick a test to fix
prompt Using the output from analyze-test-results, select the single failing test that would give the greatest improvement when fixed. Justify your choice and outline a brief fix strategy.
after analyze-test-results

agent generate-fix
title Generate a fix
prompt You are an expert in Coil and Raylib. Given `test-results.log`, the file `src/main.coil`, and the selected test from pick-test-to-fix, write a concrete code patch that resolves the failure. Explain how your change addresses the root cause.
after pick-test-to-fix

agent review-fix
title Review the fix
prompt Review the proposed patch from generate-fix against `src/main.coil` and `src/workflow.coil`. Assess correctness, Coil style, and potential side effects. Suggest any necessary improvements.
after generate-fix

approval approve-fix
title Approve the fix
after review-fix

agent verify-fix
title Verify fix and reflect
prompt After the fix is applied and tests re-run, read the new `test-results.log`. Confirm that all tests now pass. Reflect on the patterns that caused the failure and note any preventative measures for the future.
after approve-fix
